NODEJS frameworks:

Express : Middleware
        --> API
        --> authentication
        --> authorization
        --> validation
        --> upload image
        --> ...

SocketIO : observer


Loopback 3: observer + Middleware
        --> logic
        --> authentication

Loopback 4 (active) + NestJS (LTS): IoC (inversion of Control) dependency injection
        --> route, controller, repository, model
        --> service --> inject